<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你對園藝有興趣嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很喜歡<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />他販售的灌木呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說灌木只會在固定的時期開花喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯，<delay20 />簡直就像<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無法回頭的戀愛一樣。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有在<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />那購買過花卉種子嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你想改變<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
給人的印象，請務必買來試試看。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他所販售的種子都很稀有，<delay20 />種出來的花，<delay20 />
應該能讓你看見新的景色，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要每天幫花澆水，<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偶爾會綻放出
有著稀有顏色的花喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這或許是花兒們打算向我們傳達訊息呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是「我愛你」之類的……</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在是地球日的活動期間，<delay20 />
你是否有為大自然，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />盡自己的一份心力呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想要愛人的話，就先愛上大自然吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我們都接受著大自然的恩惠啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是地球日，<delay20 />你也試著在平時走慣的路上
停下腳步，<delay20 />然後眺望附近的景色吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會發現那些平時不起眼的存在，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如盛開的花朵以及充滿生命力的雜草，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都有著生命且扮演著各自的角色喔。</message>
